.	<a href="#38r">Return</a><p><a name="39"><li>Ibid.	<a href="#39r">Return</a><p><a name="40"><li>Cited in Samuel Rosenman, ed., The Public Papers and	Addresses of Franklin D. Roosevelt (New York: Random House, 1938-50),	p. 750.		<a href="#40r">Return</a></ol><HR NOSHADE><CENTER>[<A HREF="#TOP">Top of Page</A>]</CENTER><HR NOSHADE><center><P>&copy; 1995 - The Universal Salvage Corporation</p><I>Specialists in Dying Civilizations</I></center><HR NOSHADE><p>For information on The Freedom Server&copy; please contact the <a href="mailto:administrator@freedom-server.co.uk">Administrator</a></p></p><hr><p>The URL of this page is:</p><CENTER>&lt;http://www.freedom-server.co.uk/Economc-Fascism.html&gt; </CENTER><HR NOSHADE></BODY></HTML>
