dise was excluded: segmented	flat panel displays; matrix addressed flat panel displays with	less than 120,000 pixels; and cathode ray tubes (CRTs).  55 Fed. Reg.	33147, August 14, 1990, reprinted in Pub. 2311, supra , at B-5.		<a href="#141r">Return</a><p><a name="142"><li>United States International Trade Commission,	High-Information Content Flat Panel Displays and Subassemblies	Thereof From Japan, Determination of the Commission in Investigation	No. 731-TA-469 (Preliminary) Under the Tariff Act of 1930, Together	With the Information Obtained in the Investigation, Pub. 2311,	September, 1990, hereinafter referred to as Pub. 2311.		<a href="#142r">Return</a><p><a name="143"><li>55 Fed. Reg. 30042, July 24, 1990, reprinted in	Pub. 2311, supra at B-2; 55 Fed. Reg. 33146, August 14, 1990,	reprinted in Pub. 2311, supra, at B-4.		<a href="#143r">Return</a><p><a name="144"><li>55 Fed. Reg. 33146, August 14, 1990, reprinted in	Pub. 2311, supra, at B-4.		<a href="#144r">Return</a><p><a name="145"><li>55 Fed. Reg. 33146, August 14, 1990, reprinted in	Pub. 2311, supra, at B-4.		<a href="#145r">Return</a><p><a name="146"><li>55 Fed. Reg. 33146, August 14, 1990, reprinted in	Pub. 2311, supra, at B-4.		<a href="#146r">Return</a><p><a name="147"><li>Pub. 2311, supra, at 1.	<a href="#147r">Return</a><p><a name="148"><li>Pub. 2311, supra, at 5.	<a href="#148r">Return</a><p><a name="149"><li>Pub. 2311, supra, at 5-6.	<a href="#149r">Return</a><p><a name="150"><li>Pub. 2311, supra, at 6; United States	International Trade Commission, Certain All-Terrain Vehicles	from Japan, Investigation No. 731-TA-388 (Final), Pub. 2163 at	7-8, March, 1989; United States International Trade Commission,	Internal Combustion Engine Forklift Trucks from Japan, Investigation	No. 731-TA-377 (Final), Pub. 2082, at 9-11, May, 1988.		<a href="#150r">Return</a><p><a name="151"><li>Pub. 2311, supra, at 6.  The USITC pointed out	that differences in techno