/A>]</CENTER><HR NOSHADE><CENTER>&copy: 1995 - The Universal Salvage Corporation<P><I>Specialists in Dying Civilizations</I></P></CENTER><HR><B>Contact Information:</B><BR><p><a href="mailto:administrator@freedom-server.co.uk"> administrator</a></p><hr><P>The URL of this page is:</P><CENTER>&lt;http://www.freedom-server.co.uk/Dumont-Mission.html&gt;</CENTER><HR NOSHADE></BODY></HTML>
