<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE>Conn Navigational Page</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffcc"><P><CENTER><IMG SRC="rule.1.jpeg" WIDTH="432" HEIGHT="9" ALIGN="BOTTOM"NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" BORDER="1"><BR><BR><IMG SRC="ct.jpeg" WIDTH="273" HEIGHT="174" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" BORDER="5"></CENTER><H1><CENTER>CONNECTICUT</CENTER></H1><B>Connecticut</B> is an area that has a lot to offer the gay and lesbiancommunity. It is not just beautiful to look at, it is very progressive andtolerant. Cities like <A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor441075">Hartford</A>,<A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor452629">New Haven</A> and <A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor459625">NewLondon</A> offer a large concentration of community members. There are plentyof shops, bars and quaint bed and breakfasts. For people that want to getaway, there are beautiful little towns like Greenwich and Mystic. Theseplaces offer beautiful scenery, and quiet surroundings. You will also findone of this country's largest gambling casinos in Ledyard that attractsbig name entertainers such as Aretha Franklin. Whatever you need can befound in Connecticut. <H2><CENTER>Major Cities</CENTER></H2><P><CENTER><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor441075">Hartford</A><BR><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor452629">New Haven</A><BR><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor459625">New London</A></CENTER><H2>Additional Listings by cities:</H2><BR><B><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor426369">STATEWIDE</A></B> <UL>  <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor426500">AIDS </A>  <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor427498">Bars </A>  <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor427699">Funeral </A>  <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor428045">Helpline </A>  <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor429248">Political </A>  <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor430282">Professional</A>   <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor430580">Religion</A>   <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor431010">Sports</A>   <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor431176">Support </A>  <LI><A HREF="ct.list.html#anchor432414">Social</A> 