<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE>NH Nav</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffcc"><P><CENTER><IMG SRC="rule.1.jpeg" WIDTH="432" HEIGHT="9" ALIGN="BOTTOM"NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" BORDER="1"><BR><BR><IMG SRC="new.hampshire.jpeg" WIDTH="107" HEIGHT="201" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" BORDER="5"></CENTER><H1><CENTER>NEW HAMPSHIRE</CENTER></H1>New Hampshire is known for its many beautiful lakes and superb skiing conditions.Concord, Manchester and Porsmouth all have a large concentration of gayand lesbian residents. The Winter offers the majesty of The White Mountains,for those who like to ski. However, for those who enjoy escaping winterswrath next to a warm fire, you will find an abundance of rustic inns, b&amp; bs and other hideaways. The Spring and Summer offer crystal lakes,scenic views and enough nature trails and challenging terrain to satisfythe most finicky of nature lovers. The foliage offered in the fall willtake your breath away and make you realize the power and beauty of MotherNature. Shoppers beware, you never know what you may find in the shops ofPortsmouth, North Conway and all over the state. If you don't already livein New Hampshire, one trip might make you consider moving. <BR><BR><B><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor911276">STATEWIDE</A></B> <UL>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor911441">AIDS/HIV+</A>   <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor911589">Hotlines </A>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor912764">Legal </A>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor913400">Media </A>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor913512">Men's </A>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor913636">Sports </A>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor913782">Tattoos </A>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor914384">Women </A>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor914502">Youth </A></UL><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor914710"><B>AMHERST</B></A> <UL>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor915037">Youth </A></UL><A HREF="nh.list.html#anchor915603"><B>BARTLET</B></A><B> </B><UL>  <LI><A HREF="nh.list.html#anc