<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE>RI nav</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffcc"><P><CENTER><IMG SRC="rule.3.jpeg" ALIGN="BOTTOM" BORDER="1"><BR><BR><IMG SRC="ri.jpeg" WIDTH="141" HEIGHT="184" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" BORDER="5"></CENTER><H1><CENTER>RHODE ISLAND</CENTER></H1>Rhode Island may be the smallest state in the union, but it has a largeamount of activities and attractions for the gay and lesbian community.For those who want the quiet &quot;Martha Stewart&quot; life, there arethe peaceful communities of Southern Rhode Island including one of New England'sbest weekend getaways, Block Island. However, for all those who enjoy citylife, Providence is the city. It is small enough to navigate without a car.It also offers some of the best gay nightclubs in New England, most of whichare close enough to bar hop within a night. In addition, Providence hassome of the best dining in the area. The city attracts people from Bostonand Hartford areas because it is only a short drive away.<BR><BR><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor688274">STATE WIDE</A> </B><UL>  <LI><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor691130"><B>Accommodation </B></A>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor691277">AIDS/HIV 1</A> </B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor692239">Auto Dealer/Service </A></B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor692392">Business Group </A></B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor692571">Baths </A></B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor102310">Bath Supplies</A> </B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor763624">Computer Bull. Boards</A></B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor107268">Door and Cabinet</A> </B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor112550">Flowers</A> </B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor693238">Funding </A></B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor693397">Funeral </A></B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor693793">Hotlines </A></B>  <LI><B><A HREF="ri.listings.html#anchor694696">Legal </A></B